Class CalendarFieldPeriodInput

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Input<CalendarFieldSplitPeriod>

    public class CalendarFieldPeriodInput
extends MultiInput<CalendarFieldSplitPeriod,Input>
    Composite input for a CalendarFieldSplitPeriod Sub inputs are:
    • start - start-time
    • field - Calendar field
    • splits - number of sub-periods
    • count - multiple of field in sub-period
    Default start time is midnight at the start of the previous month.

    various time fields can be suppressed by passing a Calendar field value to the constructor. Only those fields greater or equal to this value are shown. The year value is always shown.

    Note we can use setStartTime(Calendar) to set Calendar fields below the finest field shown in the input.
